                "# __Useful macros for daily life in Eorzea__\r\n \r\n## Non-combat macros\r\n \r\n### :blue_car: Ride any pillion of the current target\r\n```\r\n/macroerror off\r\n/ridepillion <2>\r\n/ridepillion <3>\r\n/ridepillion <4>\r\n/ridepillion <5>\r\n/ridepillion <6>\r\n/ridepillion <7>\r\n/ridepillion <8>\r\n/micon \"Jump\" general\r\n```\r\n\r\n### :man_walking: Follow nearest player\r\n```\r\n/targetpc\r\n/follow\r\n/micon \"Flex\" emote\r\n```\r\n### :man_in_manual_wheelchair:  Sprint macro\r\nMount + Sprint + Peloton + Fate Level Sync\r\n```\r\n/macroerror off\r\n/actionerror off\r\n/ac \"Mount Roulette\"\r\n/ac \"Sprint\"\r\n/ac \"Peloton\"\r\n/levelsync on\r\n/micon \"Sprint\"\r\n```\r\n### :man_cook: Job change\r\nUseful with gatherers for activate buffs or for use difrent titles or glamours on jobs.\r\n\r\n:fishing_pole_and_fish: (Fisher example)\r\n```\r\n/micon \"Abroader Otter\" minion\r\n/gs equip XX YY\r\n/wait 1\r\n/ac \"Collect\"\r\n/title set \"Of the Irresistible Lure\"\r\n```\r\nXX = number of job on your gearset\r\nYY = number of glamor plate to apply (OPTIONAL)\r\n\r\nAlso you can make a macro for copy the crafters hotbars then you can have same skill order on each craftrer:\r\nOn the example Carpenter have all skills sorted on hotbars 1, 2, 3 and 4\r\n```\r\n/micon 25 gearset\r\n/gs equip 25 <wait.1>\r\n/hotbar copy crp 1 current 1\r\n/hotbar copy crp 2 current 2\r\n/hotbar copy crp 3 current 3\r\n/hotbar copy crp 4 current 4\r\n/title set \"Of Countless Crafts\"\r\n```\r\n### :shushing_face: Mute game (on/off)\r\n```/mastervolume```",
