                "## :crossed_swords: Combat macros\r\n\r\n### :hand_splayed: Action cast\r\n`/ac \"action or skill name\" <XX>` (<XX> its a placeholder and is optional)\r\nFor use Duty Action I and II => `/gaction \"Duty Action I\" <XX>` (<XX> its a placeholder and is optional)\r\n\r\n__Placeholders__\r\n- <t> target (used if you put nothing)\r\n- <mo> Mouse over\r\n- <f> Focus\r\n- <tt> Target of terget\r\n- <X> X = Number of party member\r\n- <lt> Last target\r\n\r\n__Mark placeholders__\r\n- <attackX> X = Target attack marks (1 to 8) \r\n- <bindX> X = Target bind marks (1 to 3) \r\n- <stopX> X = Target stop marks (1 to 2) \r\n- <square> Target square mark\r\n- <circle> Target circle mark\r\n- <cross> Target cross mark\r\n- <triangle> Target triangle mark\r\n\r\n:mouse_three_button: _Mouse over or current target example:_\r\nGives prio to mouse over, if have nothing on mouse over then do target cast.\r\n```\r\n/macroerror off\r\n/actionerror off\r\n/ac \"Cure\" <mo>\r\n/ac \"Cure\"\r\n/micon \"Cure\"\r\n```\r\n### :orange_circle: Instant ground AoE\r\nYou need have enabled `Press action twice to execute` that is located on `Main menu > System > Character Configuration > Control Settings > Target`.\r\n```\r\n/ac \"Asylum\"\r\n/ac \"Asylum\"\r\n/micon \"Asylum\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n### :clock9: Share recast timer\r\n```\r\n/p Swiftcast: <recast.Swiftcast>\r\n```",
