                "## HUD edit\r\nWe can edit HUD typing `/hudlayout` or going to `Main menu > System > HUD Layout`.\r\n### Useful tips\r\n- For enable/disable any element you can right click on it when editing HUD.\r\n- For precise placement you can select that you want move and use keyboard numeric pad arrows.\r\n- If you have something overlaped and you can't select just use the list: `Current UI Element`.\r\n- You can make biger or smaller any element also edit transparency.\r\n- Save your current UI on other slot as backup before you edit if you can.\r\n- Remember do a backup on character selection menu\r\n# How to make target cast bar bigger\r\nWe can split target HP bar, Cast bar and Status. Then we can edit each size.",
