                "## HUD Macros\r\n### Alternate the visivility of Hotbars\r\n_ __ All settings that can be set on: `on` or `off`, you can use `[on/off]` for elternate __ _\r\n\r\n```\r\n/hotbar display XX [on/off]\r\n```\r\n```\r\n/hud \"HotbarXX\" [on/off]\r\n```\r\nXX = the number of hotbar you want alternate\r\n\r\n### Change HUD Layout\r\n```\r\n/hudlayout X\r\n```\r\nX = number of layout to select (1 to 4)\r\n\r\n### Alternate the visivility of UI elements\r\n```\r\n/hud \"XXX\" [on/off]\r\n```\r\n\r\nXXX Element of UI\r\nList is bit long, you can see the name of elements while you are editing HUD or look [Lodestone List](<https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/playguide/db/text_command/be2b72ee3f6/>)\r\n_quotation marks are mandatory if its more than one word_\r\nExample:\r\n`/hud \"Party List\" [on/off]`\r\n\r\nExample of HUD alternate macro\r\n```\r\n/hud \"Hotbar1\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"Hotbar2\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"Hotbar3\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"Hotbar4\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"Gil\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"param\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"plist\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"JobGauge1\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"JobGauge2\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"ServerInfo\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"ExpBar\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"sfx\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"sienh\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"sicenh\" [on/off]\r\n/hud \"dlist\" [on/off]\r\n```\r\nThis macro hide/show:\r\n-  4 hotbars\r\n- Gil\r\n- HP/Mana bars\r\n- Party list\r\n- Job gauges\r\n- Server info (clock, server bar)\r\n- Experience bar\r\n- Duty List (quests, fates)\r\n- Status info bars (Buffs debufs)"

